title: RIVER PHOENIX WAS HERE (A Documentary By JSK) Part 2 of 4
description:
RIVER PHOENIX WAS HERE 
is a non-profit Documentary, Written, Narrated, Produced, Directed with an Original Music Score & songs by Jason Stuart Kamasz (JSK). 
The film has been created to chronicle the life and legacy of actor, musician and humanitarian River Phoenix.
